<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>President Appointment</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #3949ab;
      color: white;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0;
    }
    .content {
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
      padding: 25px;
      border-left: 1px solid #ddd;
      border-right: 1px solid #ddd;
    }
    .footer {
      background-color: #f1f1f1;
      padding: 15px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: #666;
      border-radius: 0 0 5px 5px;
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
    }
    .highlight {
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #3949ab;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #3949ab;
      color: white;
      padding: 12px 25px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 4px;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Congratulations!</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Dear <%= name %>,</p>
      
      <p>We're pleased to inform you that you have been appointed as the <span class="highlight">President</span> of the newly created organization: <span class="highlight"><%= organizationName %></span>.</p>
      
      <p>As the President, you will be responsible for leading the organization and working closely with your staff advisor, <%= advisorName %>.</p>
      
      <p>Key responsibilities include:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Organizing and presiding over meetings</li>
        <li>Planning and coordinating events</li>
        <li>Representing the organization to the campus community</li>
        <li>Managing organization resources and budget</li>
      </ul>
      
      <p>Please log in to the EventLink platform to access your organization's dashboard.</p>
      
      <center><a href="<%= loginUrl %>" class="button">Access Your Dashboard</a></center>
      
      <p>If you have any questions, please don't hesitate to contact the administration or your staff advisor.</p>
      
      <p>Best regards,<br>
      The EventLink Team</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>This is an automated message. Please do not reply directly to this email.</p>
      <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> EventLink. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>